bio: Bimsha is currently working for Profoundis Labs Pvt Ltd handling Partnerships and Business Development. She is truly passionate about her work and is always eager to connect with other marketers.She enjoy all aspects of her job, her favorite stage of a project is working with the client or business unit leader to understand his or her business objectives. As she go through that collaborative process, the ideas start to flow and that’s always the fun part. Bimsha had completed her B.tech from KMCTCE (Calicut University affiliated) and schooling from Spring valley School NITC campus. Bimsha love to link with people. She is an Artist. And was on track for last 18 years.She is interested in engineering, robotics.etc. Bimsha started her career as a Lecturer in Embedded Engineering at Arvin Technologies, where she trained around 200 Engineers then she worked as a Business Development Officer at Cybrosys Technologies Pvt Ltd a software company and was lucky enough to work with amazing clients She also volunteered at IEEE (World’s largest technical organization) and gained a lot from it, Lots of links and experience.
